# Admin Portal

- Admin sidebar: Overview, Subjects & Exams, Sessions, Monitor, Results, Reports, Settings.
- Layout: fixed dark navy sidebar (220px), gold primary actions.
- Subjects hierarchy: Subject → Exam → Question Bank (3-level drill-down).
- Sessions can combine exams from multiple subjects; each session has a unique `examCode`.
- Exam instructions textarea shown to students as popup before exam.
- Admin login at `/admin/login`; dashboard at `/admin/*`.
- Student Management tab deferred for V1.
